AngloGold Ashanti to Buy Stake in First Uranium from Village Main Reef

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-22T06:41:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/anglogold-ashanti-to-buy-stake-in-first-uranium-from-village-main-reef.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG)  will buy a
19.79 percent stake in  First Uranium Corp. (FIU)  held by Vilage Main
Reef Ltd. for 205 million rand.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
